{"tid":437861,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"做左N年外國代購代運，你問我答(二)","createTime":"2017-10-16T11:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T00:47:13.000Z","uid":60483,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"59b00d974196301a6fec18457f10d9d62f024674","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"之前1001前文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/93751/page/41?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/93751/page/41?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n抱歉，因為本人呢幾個月實在太忙太累，所以到而家先可以找數，繼續回答有關代購代運既問題。<br />\n係呢段時間其實我都開左個FB Page，諗住係多個平台分享一下外國網購經驗同埋苦與樂，有興趣既可以去望下，同時希望大家多多指教／支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/murmurtwin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmurmurtwin&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ed4a3691\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/murmurtwin</a><br />\n唔係賺錢廣告，希望唔會違反版規<br />\n<br />\n同上次一樣，我係唔會係度回答有關我公司有關既跟單/落單任何正負面指控之類問題，希望大家明白同尊重，我將對呢類問題保持沉默<br />\n請大家繼續指教分享<br />\n<br />\n下面回覆將會寫一個我岩岩整好既外國PAYPAL 申請教學~ 請留意留意~"},{"pid":"ed277938f3cb254dff29533b0f414a2ddd542dbd","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"今日想同大家探討一個比較中階少少既話題，就係到底點解要/點樣申請一個其他國家/特別美國既Paypal賬戶！<br />\n<br />\n點解要申請?<br />\n<br />\n如果團友你都幾鍾意網購又或有留意我Post既話，不難發現一D公司就係點都唔鍾意自己國家貨品向外流，佢地就係唔鍾意賣俾外國人(是的，特別是鄰國朋友)，所以會千方百計阻止我地購買。好似A&amp;F果D去到極端既例子就不用了，但有D公司就係呢方面做得不太徹底(因為佢可能覺得只需要隔走一半外國人就足夠)，佢地唔會接受香港Paypal賬戶，但就係會接受香港信用卡申請既外國Paypal賬戶，所以如果團友擁有一個外國Paypal Account 的話，能購物的網站亦會增加，網購必備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/_ir60qUJdBlU3jfy8yTe9XBdRFWirbfmWP37oGtnqrFO6yvM5S6B593cTr0851HUldQ5EgGCJ2MIFVmL-BGhz9BAhxZ2bltSg51kriwWZuxk0fc1CzqQw7qghDt24hqDNolo7t5jdnjORaAuiW_Du6PB0D3W=s0-d-e1-ft#https://market.sunnny.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-624x402.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fci4.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F_ir60qUJdBlU3jfy8yTe9XBdRFWirbfmWP37oGtnqrFO6yvM5S6B593cTr0851HUldQ5EgGCJ2MIFVmL-BGhz9BAhxZ2bltSg51kriwWZuxk0fc1CzqQw7qghDt24hqDNolo7t5jdnjORaAuiW_Du6PB0D3W%3Ds0-d-e1-ft%23https%3A%2F%2Fmarket.sunnny.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D-624x402.png&h=2a2f4d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPAYPAL<br />\n當你在外國網站購買貨品並使用PAYPAL付款時，看見這類字句，即代表你需要一個該國的PAYPAL賬戶了<br />\n什麼網站不接受國際PAYPAL賬戶但接受香港卡申請的該地PAYPAL賬戶?<br />\n<br />\n例子非常多，較出名的包括：<br />\n<br />\nFinishline 美國官網 <a href=\"http://www.finishline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.finishline.com&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=fddcf0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.finishline.com</a><br />\nMichael Kors 美國官網 <a href=\"http://www.michaelkors.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.michaelkors.com&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=976e1fcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.michaelkors.com</a><br />\nDickies 美國官網 <a href=\"http://www.dickies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dickies.com%2F&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b11558a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dickies.com/</a><br />\nJimmyJazz 美國官網 <a href=\"http://www.jimmyjazz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jimmyjazz.com&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=07b011d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.jimmyjazz.com</a>"},{"pid":"a758fe7f6d50ad9435cc6ebffc749e5dd755f3fa","tid":437861,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"90fd79e4a75beca29511fef8f841a2bdd07d4a65","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/js89xi0h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjs89xi0h&h=fb477ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買野時睇到呢個表示你需要一個該地既paypal 賬號了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614ef4e557f2249e7f552ddfd54c82d9899aa314","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"外國PAYPAL申請方法<br />\n<br />\n以下的例子是申請美國PAYPAL賬戶，但任何國家都應該一律通用(因為美國自911後已成為呢方面最嚴密既國家)<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/hk/webapps/mpp/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fhk%2Fwebapps%2Fmpp%2Fhome&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=78138a16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.paypal.com/hk/webapps/mpp/home</a><br />\n進入香港的PAYPAL網站，先不要急著申請賬戶，按頁面右下角的香港區旗標誌選擇國家<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/syuhirq7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsyuhirq7&h=d1ca0959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 選擇美國<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7vn2dmo4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7vn2dmo4&h=f2115c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 選擇Sign Up -&gt; Personal Account -&gt; Next<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gx7ksmvi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgx7ksmvi&h=f6102e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 填寫真實相關資料 -&gt; NEXT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7k8fminp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7k8fminp&h=d77a721f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 地址輸入轉運地址也可以啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/75khwprx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F75khwprx&h=a92169da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Shop with paypal -&gt; get started -&gt; 輸入信用卡資料<br />\n注意: 唔係張張信用卡都可以，推薦使用AMEX較容易通過佢系統審查(VISA/MASTER 難少少)，按下Link card 後，沒出現問題就代表可以使用了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qkhvizpu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqkhvizpu&h=7e6d5c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完成! 你可以使用屬於自己的外國Paypal賬戶購物了!<br />\n總結<br />\n<br />\n有d網站其實就算使用外國Paypal賬戶，就算表面上下到訂單也好，最後還是會砍掉你的訂單的(e.g. Macy's)，你亦要留意自己申請的賬戶其實係無通過身份認證，所以會有限額的(但夠你下幾十張單)。唔想煩的話，都係請個做代購的解決吧。 <br />\n<br />\n註：其實家長用這方法付外國子女的大學學費也可以啦夠吉士夠外匯都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cb595e4c38d119eccac59e7fdc3076be95c156","tid":437861,"uid":104339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"巴打忙左幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe021bd3c79c646c3a1a3d96311f57f2cc49ca0","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打忙左幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀而家都係唔得閒，又有同事走又搬鋪"},{"pid":"808219c5c315219035145dee782c19f93d1065f6","tid":437861,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"想請教巴打如果係dickies 官網買野寄香港貴唔貴呀？係咪直接用visa比錢就得架啦"},{"pid":"86e5bcd20d117bc9d8622cd6154260bfc55611c1","tid":437861,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"感恩節果輪  名牌通常會唔會有減價？if 有，減得多唔多？<br />\ne.g. burberry / BV"},{"pid":"13dd971e65af482571be418c08e1826ea5696028","tid":437861,"uid":73854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T19:21:44.000Z","msg":"團購仲有得做？"},{"pid":"da9a4e759dde6e58d29bb97f7012f7687d118e0a","tid":437861,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bc3e3192a04e4cf9f00a0ed5c5d6d027f6950647","tid":437861,"uid":153759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T01:05:41.000Z","msg":"想由美國運少少野去香港<br />\n咩途徑最抵？"},{"pid":"5d187da88ab9cbae7ac41e61b9701d2b9859617e","tid":437861,"uid":74687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":