ote><br />\n巴打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/nottday\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnottday&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a7bff27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nottday</a><br />\n有興趣可以一齊傾傾</blockquote><br />\nSay左hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198c371c8fec839e8773826a1b738eeb733e4a63","tid":437861,"uid":20759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"想問問Nike US 同 Adidas US 呢啲會Cut單嘅網站有咩方法搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44c9c9f0d1e7e74340c15e765fd54f6164c909b","tid":437861,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Levis us係咪已經冇辦法集運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外有冇代購網會賣假貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我落到單wo ship 埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7a04f8ad30da0075a3bce7ebc30e91b3300c8c","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感恩節果輪  名牌通常會唔會有減價？if 有，減得多唔多？<br />\ne.g. burberry / BV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣會減，唔減果個應該唔係美國網站黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881a48796cd81c50d4b435d4186ec4941255c850","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>團購仲有得做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇你做d乜，如果淘寶就算啦，但你如果係某某國家發現好野，對方又肯大大堆幫你運既，咁就ok<br />\n<br />\n利申以前係環球影城運過幾百支可樂"},{"pid":"4b81ddb4516d9dc7393eabe41f4a24fdc69de0f0","tid":437861,"uid":60483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"